attributes.Long form description: The student wants to remove the Joy-Con from the Nintendo Switch, and the instructor tells him how to do it. The student then mounts the Joy-Con to the comfort grip. Next, he removes the Joy-Con from the comfort grip and attaches the Joy-Con straps to the controllers. After that, he removes the Joy-Con straps and reinserts the Joy-Con into the Nintendo Switch. The student then tries to stand the Nintendo Switch using the kickstand but has trouble finding it, so the instructor shows him how to do it. Finally, the student switches the game card and SD card on the Nintendo Switch.
